<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Contact Us - SpinCycle Laundry</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #1a202c;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #1a202c;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .navbar .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .navbar .brand a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .navbar ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
        }
        
        .navbar ul li a {
            color: #1a202c;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .navbar ul li a:hover,
        .navbar ul li a.active {
            color: #667eea;
        }
        
        .navbar .auth {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        
        .navbar .auth a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .navbar .auth a:first-child {
            color: #667eea;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .navbar .auth a:first-child:hover {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .navbar .auth a:last-child {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .navbar .auth a:last-child:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .main-content {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
            background: white;
            border-radius: 32px 32px 0 0;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .contact-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            padding: 30px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .contact-info h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .info-icon {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-top: 3px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .info-content h3 {
            color: #1a202c;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .info-content p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        
        .info-content a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .info-content a:hover {
            color: #764ba2;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .contact-form {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .contact-form h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #1a202c;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        
        input,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: #1a202c;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        input:focus,
        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
        }
        
        textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }
        
        .submit-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .submit-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .submit-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #1a202c;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            
            .contact-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            
            .navbar ul {
                gap: 16px;
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }
            
            .main-content {
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="brand">
            <a href="/">üåÄ SpinCycle</a>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="active">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="auth">
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/register">Register</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">We'd love to hear from you. Get in touch with us today!</p>

            <div class="contact-wrapper">
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-icon">üìç</div>
                        <div class="info-content">
                            <h3>Location</h3>
                            <p>123 Laundry Lane<br>Clean City, CC 12345</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-icon">üìû</div>
                        <div class="info-content">
                            <h3>Phone</h3>
                            <p><a href="tel:+1234567890">+1 (234) 567-8900</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-icon">üìß</div>
                        <div class="info-content">
                            <h3>Email</h3>
                            <p><a href="mailto:support@spincycle.com">support@spincycle.com</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-icon">üïê</div>
                        <div class="info-content">
                            <h3>Business Hours</h3>
                            <p>Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br>
                            Sat - Sun: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-form">
                    <h2>Send us a Message</h2>
                    <form>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">Full Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone">
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="subject">Subject</label>
                            <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="message">Message</label>
                            <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        
                        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p><strong>SpinCycle Laundry</strong></p>
                <p>Making your life easier, one spin at a time.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.85em; color: #aaa;">¬© 2025 SpinCycle Laundry. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
